  "texts": [
    "To prevent the model from experiencing hallucinatory effects that could lead to incorrect guidance for users, we removed drugs with unknown attributes, retaining only 326 records unknown labels.",
    "Inspired by the \"Self-chatting\" approach in Baize 39, we employed ChatGLM for data augmentation of our processed dataset.",
    "As a result, we generated five additional sentences that maintain a similar meaning and intent to the original patient's complaints in the dataset.",
    "These new sentences were then added to the dataset, resulting in a six-fold expansion of the dataset.",
    "In addition, to ensure the rationality and safety of CPM usage, we invited two senior clinical practitioners of TCM with advanced professions to review the CPMI dataset, further enhancing the quality and effectiveness of the dataset."
  ],
